Last Updated: April 17, 2023
This section provides additional details regarding the Personal Information that we collect or process about Colorado, Virginia, Utah and Connecticut residents, and describes your rights pursuant to the Colorado Privacy Act, Virginia Consumer Data Protection Act, the Utah Consumer Privacy Act and Connecticut Data Privacy Act.
