1. Your Rights
Under Colorado, Virginia, Connecticut and Utah law, users who are residents of these states have specific rights regarding their Personal Information. These rights are subject to certain exceptions described below. When required, we will respond to most requests within 45 days unless it is reasonably necessary to extend the response time. Subject to certain limitations, you have the following rights:
