Last Updated: September 2022
Stanley Black & Decker, Inc. along with its affiliated entities including the company to which you are applying for employment (collectively, “Stanley Black & Decker”, “SBD” “us”, “our”, “we”), values your trust and is committed to the responsible management, use and protection of Personal Information. This Candidate Privacy Notice (“
Notice
”) describes our practices regarding the collection, use and disclosure of any Personal Information collected during a job or internship application process (either online or offline) or through the Careers section of our website (located at
Careers | Stanley Black & Decker (stanleyblackanddecker.com)
) (“
Careers Site
”) (collectively the “
Application Material
”). Personal Information submitted on other Stanley Black & Decker’s websites or through the use of our products and services will be used in accordance with our general online Stanley Black & Decker
Global Privacy Policy
. Please note that this Notice does not apply to any third-party websites, services or applications.
